             was indicted for <rs id="t17730217-50-off249" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17730217-50-off249" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730217-50-off249" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing thirty glass bottles, value 5 s. thirteen quarts of Madeira wine, value 30 s. thirteen quarts of Port wine, value 28 s. one quart of white Port wine, value 1 s. 6 d. one quart of Lisbon wine, value 1 s. 6 d. and one pint of Hungary wine, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17730217-50-victim442" type="victimName">
                     Robert
                      Ireland
                  <interp inst="t17730217-50-victim442" type="surname" value="Ireland"></interp>
